#how to add add to cart button in collection page
#how to add add to cart button in quick view

https://help.shopify.com/en/themes/customization/products/add-to-cart/replace-add-to-cart-button
https://nerdbugs.com  (broklen theme)
      
                 <form method="post" action="/cart/add">
  <input type="hidden" name="id" value="{{ product.variants.first.id }}" />
    
  <input type="submit" value="Add to cart" class="btn" />
</form> 
